          "description": "I check in 2 days ago because I had an issue with glass, the front reception pointed me to sign in and it was really easy as well as them being very friendly! As well doctor and the nurse themselves. It was a quiet morning so I didn't have to wait to long and left feeling 100% better when the glass was removed, 10/10 would go again if anything urgent is needed",
