          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtxrQkLUcVRa1GKd4n0k_wc3rcQPYkvRb7qt5MhiznexHPizP6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "EDITED: Removing a star because it is impossible to call this location. I missed a call regarding lab results and have called back five times throughout their open hours and no one ever picks up.\n\nWalked in close to when they opened and was seen pretty quickly. Their registration/check in system is pretty much all digital, which I didn\u2019t love as it couldn\u2019t accurately process my insurance and I ended up having to just speak to the receptionist anyway. I saw others also having insurance issues. The lobby was also boiling hot, which did not help me feel less nauseous. However, once I was seen, the practitioners were very kind and efficient. Nurse Carmen made me feel very comfortable and like I was in good hands, and the doctor I saw quickly addressed my issue and called in a prescription to my pharmacy. She also called me after my visit to ensure I knew how to use the prescription, which I appreciated. Once you get seen, the medical team is very good.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KdlVYQmxVMGxKUVZSVWREWkpVell0T0ZGdk5IYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x96d01be4b88995db!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnJvUXBlU0lJQVRUdDZJUzYtOFFvNHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
