          "description": "The doctor i saw today was very caring and understanding. The docs  assistant was direct to my needs who took a strep and covid test on me. The receptionist seemed busy with alot of things going on but somehow managed to to be versatile and professional with everyone from the phone calls to ppl in the waiting room asking questions/needs. I walked in at 9am and walked out 30 min later the process was fast and efficient. There was no issues with payments as i had my insurance cover this with my $15 copay.i would definitely recommend this place.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZd2FXUmZhR2R2Y1d4NlowRk9aRWx5ZW5sSmNtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x96d01be4b88995db!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkYwaWRfaGdvcWx6Z0FOZElyenlJcmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
