          "description": "The staff at Medrite are always very polite and professional. The patient's well being is always a priority to them. I have and will continue to recommend them to my family and friends.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0RWNIUnpjRUpGYTNGTlVHSXdZVkF0UTNsNVZWRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x96d01be4b88995db!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOktEcHRzcEJFa3FNUGIwYVAtQ3l5VVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
