          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQFHWlJU_a1g0B4LUpqNb64cVSwpdvOFvIU5yoCnrh6nkfPVPeSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "honestly i am always weary about urgent care places because ive had bad experiences, but my time here today was so amazing! the PA was so sweet and listened to my concerns thoroughly, and the ladies at the front were extremely kind! I felt so comfortable coming here. I was in and out of here in less than 30 minutes. I would recommend this MedRite 100%! thank you to all the ladies who helped me today!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SSE1XUlhTbEYzUzNoUlNrWjJSSE5SZUZwMFgwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x96d01be4b88995db!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnRHMWRXSlF3S3hRSkZ2RHNReFp0X0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "6 months ago",
